36
00:02:58.230 --> 00:03:04.210
And also came up with the use cases for
heterodyne receiver and

37
00:03:04.210 --> 00:03:09.400
transmitter, which is really what
made the broadcast industry happen.

38
00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:13.040
And he was selling his
rights to Westinghouse and

39
00:03:13.040 --> 00:03:16.556
RCA, and he was making really good money.

40
00:03:16.556 --> 00:03:22.286
The broadcast industry had taken off.

41
