make De Forest's tube work
much better than De Forest.

57
00:04:49.790 --> 00:04:53.760
He had come to the same
conclusion as AT&T did,

58
00:04:53.760 --> 00:04:58.670
that you did not need a gas in there,
you needed vacuum.

59
00:04:58.670 --> 00:05:04.530
And by reorganizing the amplifier
as a feedback generator,

60
00:05:04.530 --> 00:05:11.520
you could have a radio transmitter and
a receiver.

61
00:05:11.520 --> 00:05:15.732
So both RCA and Sarnoff and
the content and

62
00:05:15.732 --> 00:05:20.548
consumer electronics
industry benefited a lot

63
00:05:20.548 --> 00:05:25.040
from Edwin Armstrong's inventions.

64
00:05:25.040 --> 00:05:31.200
This is a picture of Armstrong and
