106
00:09:18.256 --> 00:09:22.950
His wife, Marion MacInnis,
after his death,

107
00:09:22.950 --> 00:09:28.770
was able to establish the ownership
of some of his patents, and

108
00:09:28.770 --> 00:09:34.590
